ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent perforation of the uterus.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Diagnosis. The intent of this data element is to identify perforation of the uterus.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with codes identifying perforations of the uterus. This is a grouping of ICD-10-CM codes and SNOMED CT codes .),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that pertain to perforation to body structures other than the uterus.)
